(1, 'The products of electrolysis of aqueous sodium chloride in Down''s process is are', 'hydrogen at cathode and chlorine at anode ', 'hydrogen at cathode and oxygen at anode', 'sodium at cathode and oxygen at anode', 'sodium at cathode and chlorine at anode', 'In Down''s process electrolysis of aqueous NaCl gives Na at cathode and Cl<sub>2</sub> at anode.', '0', 'A'),
