(4, 'The bleaching action of SO<sub>2</sub> 	is due to', 'reduction', 'dehydration ', 'polymerization', 'Oxidation', '<br>SO<sub>2</sub> acts as bleaching agent as well as antichlor. e.g.</br> <br> $ SO_2 + 2H_20 +Cl_2 \\rightarrow H_2SO_4 + 2HCl $ </br> <br> $ SO_2 + 2H_20 \\longrightarrow H_2SO_4 + 2H $  </br> <br> Hence, bleaching actions is due to oxidation and it is permanent. </br>', '0', 'A'),
